Panthyria is a willing and eager warrior. She doesn't
make friends easily, but if you get close to her you
will have a friend for life. She likes to fight, and
she is good at it, armed with her Magna Pulse Cannons,
(3 shots from one of those and your wasted!)she is
always ready for battle, she doesn't learn to trust
ppl quickly, and is suspicious about almost
everything, Extremely intelligent, and always thinks
things through! She is quick to help others, and
beleives that a life lost for no reason is a waste of
a creation.She likes to challenge herself, and be
better than the best.
